    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Retail Simulator, you start out with a small plot, pocket change, and a dream. Slowly gain revenue by selling a wide range of categorized products, from a Teddy Bear to a Gaming Keyboard! Expand your store, hire employees, level up and become the biggest retail store of all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/ac2cac4d2e47e90606aed4359ffaaa29.webp?t=1762406299\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter build mode with a top-down view, precision place shelves and racks or use grid mode. Place walls, windows, lights, and sliding doors to your liking. Build a custom floor layout that suites your needs. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/6f0f8d66c0f3013a94afa1e8448244fb.poster.avif?t=1762406299\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/6f0f8d66c0f3013a94afa1e8448244fb.webm?t=1762406299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/6f0f8d66c0f3013a94afa1e8448244fb.mp4?t=1762406299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/be15c116d5574e33a4791cce88390877.webp?t=1762406299\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Developed with friends in mind, you can build, manage, and thrive with yourself and up to 3 other people. Use Steam overlay to invite or join.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/11d968489a654d159056f163629e5559.poster.avif?t=1762406299\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/11d968489a654d159056f163629e5559.webm?t=1762406299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/11d968489a654d159056f163629e5559.mp4?t=1762406299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/d4889d58e77a1a9377c2842c38776de4.webp?t=1762406299\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add products to your shopping cart via the mobile tablet, place an order and await the delivery truck! Make sure storage racks are assigned so restockers can move inventory around.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/26e9a4108669983eb344ae8c02c7e52e.poster.avif?t=1762406299\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/26e9a4108669983eb344ae8c02c7e52e.webm?t=1762406299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/26e9a4108669983eb344ae8c02c7e52e.mp4?t=1762406299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/057b8d239ae8d212a4bdb0e96f2e1568.webp?t=1762406299\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assign products to shelves by restocking with a product box. Click the tag and set your price! Be mindful that Customers will not buy overpriced items.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/a82b6ec5004a3eda964c4dc760a975af.poster.avif?t=1762406299\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/a82b6ec5004a3eda964c4dc760a975af.webm?t=1762406299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203280/extras/a82b6ec5004a3eda964c4dc760a975af.mp4?t=1762406299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
